  "notes": [
    "This study examined ethnic disparities in male breast cancer between Han and Mongolian populations in Inner Mongolia, China",
    "The study found minimal ethnic disparities in disease burden and healthcare utilization, with the exception of higher 5-year prevalence in Mongolians and higher chemotherapy usage",
    "Economic factors were identified as potentially important drivers of disparities"
